017package ninja.leaping.configurate.objectmapping;
018
019/**
020 * Exception thrown on errors encountered while mapping objects
021 */
022public class ObjectMappingException extends Exception {
023    public static final long serialVersionUID = 7549002182650685930L;
024    public ObjectMappingException() {
025        super();
026    }
027
028    public ObjectMappingException(String message) {
029        super(message);
030    }
031
032    public ObjectMappingException(String message, Throwable cause) {
033        super(message, cause);
034    }
035
036    public ObjectMappingException(Throwable cause) {
037        super(cause);
038    }
039
040    protected ObjectMappingException(String message, Throwable cause, boolean enableSuppression, boolean writableStackTrace) {
041        super(message, cause, enableSuppression, writableStackTrace);
042    }
043}
